prim = {
    id: node.id,
    type: node.type,
    style: node.style,
    content: node.content || "",
    secondary: node.secondary || "",
    link: node.link || "",
    flag1: node.flag1,
    margin: node.margin,
    elType: elType,
    left: node.x - node.w,
    top: node.y - node.h,
    width: node.w * 2,
    height: node.h * 2,
    x: node.x,
    y: node.y,
    w: node.w,
    h: node.h
}
